<p>+------------------------------------------+</p>
<p>+------------------------------------------+</p>
<table><tr><td>HEADER: Logo</td><td>Search</td><td>Nav (Home, Koleksi,</td></tr><tr><td>Keranjang, Pesanan, Login)</td></tr><tr><td>HERO SECTION</td></tr><tr><td>"Temukan Sepatu Impianmu"</td></tr><tr><td>CTA: Lihat Koleksi</td><td>Baca Artikel</td></tr><tr><td>BRAND RECOMMENDATION (4 brand card)</td></tr><tr><td>PRODUK REKOMENDASI (4 product card)</td></tr><tr><td>ARTIKEL TERBARU (4 article card)</td></tr><tr><td>FOOTER (Brand, Kategori, Info, Akun)</td></tr></table>
<p>[Halaman Koleksi]</p>
